@cdrtyler Hi @cdrtyler, we are sincerely sorry for the inconvenience of contacting us at this time.
We invite you to DM us with all the details of your reservation which will allow us to meet your expectations as well as possible  
Have a good day, Yvonne

@stoolierecords Hello @stoolierecords, we regret this incident at the arrival of your flight. Did you make your loss report online via https://t.co/3hkfTenx5h ?
We remain at your disposal if needed. 
Good evening, Yvonne

@Melissa12500392 Hi Melissa, uou will find the steps to take for compensation on this dedicated page of our site: https://t.co/3hkfTenx5h
We remain at your disposal, if needed! 
Have a good day, Yvonne

@JessAguirreNBC Hello Jessica, we understand your dissatisfaction.
We forwarded your feedback to our complaints department which will get back to you directly.
Yvonne

@highley_sharon Dear @highley_sharon,  
In order to assist you in the best possible way, can you please indicate the reference number of your file by private message on Messenger (for Facebook) or by DM (on Twitter)? 
Thank you, Yvonne

@JessAguirreNBC Dear @JessAguirreNBC, you can follow the progress of your luggage here: https://t.co/c7aFTJLEpd
We are still available in private messaging (TW/FB)
Have a nice evening, Yvonne
